"""
Face Animation Transfer Tool — face_main_ctrl
===============================================
Features:
  - Export a specific frame range
  - Import with a frame offset (animation starts at target frame)
  - Auto zero-key padding: keys all controls to 0 five frames before
    and five frames after the animation range on import
  - Transfers both keyed animation and static values

Usage:
    launch_ui()
"""

